Package fr.upmc.datacenter.software.applicationvm.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ApplicationVMDynamicStateI
    The interface ApplicationVMDynamicStateI defines the object behaviour of the ones representing the dynamic state of application virtual machines.
    ApplicationVMIntrospectionI
    The class ApplicationVMIntrospectionI defines the component services to introspect applicaiton virtual machines.
    ApplicationVMManagementI
    The interface ApplicationVMManagementI defines the methods to manage an application virtual machine component.
    ApplicationVMStaticStateDataI
    The interface ApplicationVMStaticStateDataI defines the data exchanges to get static information from application virtual machines.
    ApplicationVMStaticStateI
    The interface ApplicationVMStaticStateI types the data objects exchanged to get static information from application virtual machines.
    TaskI
    The interface TaskI is used to define tasks exchanged between Application VM components and Processor components to execute requests.
